  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/15500b6681a0f12c8f7d2c597ed7d530.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a future where immortality is a privilege of the wealthy, Au Revoir Ltd. dominates the market with synthetic brains capable of storing human consciousness. Sentinels are tasked with locating these minds and carrying out the recovery and transfer process into new bodies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore interactive environments, collect documents and clues, solve unique puzzles, and make decisions that influence the course of the story. Use your car to navigate different areas and interact with characters who hide more than they reveal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/dc18d9677c73455d8c7a2873aecb3705.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a rich and complex story where the narrative unfolds with depth, filled with twists and moral dilemmas that challenge your view of the world and of the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/fce00db1caf8bae0a701609eb64d8aee.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/83705877e94a8bab9f42bd48300bd1bb.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a carefully crafted futuristic world with detailed environments and striking visual design. The neon-noir atmosphere blends vibrant colors with a dense mood, creating a deeply immersive cyberpunk setting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/51b3347a2bb29fb8b11cf4ec5f0e4936.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/0431036dccc1c89e7c3c431b5f962319.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a variety of characters, each with their own personality, motivations, and hidden secrets. Conversations reveal crucial details and open up different paths, adding weight to every encounter and multiple ways to interpret what’s truly happening.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/b376584936af0d26c34be046a4a14e33.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face puzzles that require logic, observation, and attention to detail. Gather clues, connect information, and solve narrative-driven challenges. Each solved mystery brings you closer to the truth — or to new questions to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an unforgettable journey in <i>Au Revoir</i>, where every decision can alter the fate of the world.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/15500b6681a0f12c8f7d2c597ed7d530.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a future where immortality is a privilege of the wealthy, Au Revoir Ltd. dominates the market with synthetic brains capable of storing human consciousness. Sentinels are tasked with locating these minds and carrying out the recovery and transfer process into new bodies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore interactive environments, collect documents and clues, solve unique puzzles, and make decisions that influence the course of the story. Use your car to navigate different areas and interact with characters who hide more than they reveal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/dc18d9677c73455d8c7a2873aecb3705.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/f519f7fa30cd588d6e0e0b655ff07b53.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a rich and complex story where the narrative unfolds with depth, filled with twists and moral dilemmas that challenge your view of the world and of the protagonist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" s