y, motivations, and hidden secrets. Conversations reveal crucial details and open up different paths, adding weight to every encounter and multiple ways to interpret what’s truly happening.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/b376584936af0d26c34be046a4a14e33.avif?t=1764783253\" width=660 height=96 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.poster.avif?t=1764783253\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.webm?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079600/extras/2d3215d218aa696de7f6b8a5470e8b00.mp4?t=1764783253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face puzzles that require logic, observation, and attention to detail. Gather clues, connect information, and solve narrative-driven challenges. Each solved mystery brings you closer to the truth — or to new questions to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an unforgettable journey in <i>Au Revoir</i>, where every decision can alter the fate of the world.</p>",
